Whether it’s Mary and Rhoda, Woody and Buzz Lightyear, or the 20-somethings of
 “Friends,” Hollywood has long celebrated the power of friendship. And with good
 reason. A true friend gives support without judgment, comes through in a crisis
 and knows just the right thing to say when it matters most. Friendships are an
 essential ingredient in a happy life, so it’s time to give them the care and
 attention they deserve.
Keep reading to learn why friendships matter, how to sustain them and the simple
steps you can take right now to be a better friend.